  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Increases container shipping costs",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sanath Manjula, President of the All Ceylon Container Transport Union said that the container transport charges will be increased.",
        "Accordingly, the union leader added that the container transport tariff will be increased by 10 per cent with effect from midnight today.",
        "Sanath Manjula, President of the Sri Lanka Container Transport Union, said that the decision was taken due to the increase in fuel prices.",
        "Meanwhile, when the fuel price was hiked last May, the tariff on container transport was increased by 35 per cent, but again the tariff will be increased by 10 per cent."
      ],
